mpany limited markets its oil products to various sectors including transportation aviation shipping construction industrial and agriculture sectors and sells its oil products through oil traders the company was formerly known as the bangchak petroleum public company limited and changed its name to bangchak corporation public company limited in april  bangchak corporation public company limited is headquartered in bangkok thailand detailed description  m tower buildingth floorsukhumvit roadbangchak phra khanongbangkok  thailand phone     fax     wwwbangchakcoth key executives for bangchak corporation public company limited bangchak corporation public company limited does not have any key executives recorded bangchak corporation public company limited key developments bangchak corporation public company limited board meeting jul   jul   bangchak corporation public company limited board meeting jul   agenda to approve an amalgamation between bbp holding company limited bbh and kslgi company limited kslgi bangchak corporation public company limited announces change in directorship of pichai chunhavajira from chairman and nonexecutive director to chairman and independent director jun   bangchak corporation public company limited informed that the directorship of mr pichai chunhavajira is changed from chairman and nonexecutive director to chairman and independent director effective from june   bangchak corporation public company limited reports unaudited consolidated and company earnings results for the first quarter ended march   may   bangchak corporation public company limited reported unaudited consolidated and company earnings results for the first quarter ended march   for the quarter on consolidated basis the company reported revenue from sale of goods and rendering of services of thb  against thb  a year ago ebitda was thb  million against thb  million a year ago profit before finance cost and income tax expense was thb  against thb  a year ago profit before inco